title: YOU HAVE ONE LIFE
itunes:title: YOU HAVE ONE LIFE
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
Everybody dies, sooner or later, but don't worry about your death, worry about your life. Everybody dies, but not everybody truly lives. One of the Best Motivational Speeches Ever featuring Walter Bond (https://bit.ly/WalterBondMotiversity) and Coach Pain (https://bit.ly/CoachPainMotiversity).


"Every single day, live as if today was your last day."


Music by Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic).


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
